    Aircraft Info

   Airworthiness Directives All ADs from the 1940's to the present time
   Aircraft Fleet Age Information Average age of aircraft by aircraft
   group
   General Aviation Airworthiness Alerts Selected malfunctions on general
   aviation aircraft
   Amateur Built Aircraft Reference material for construction and
   operation of amateur-built aircraft
   Export Airworthiness Approval Procedures Procedures for exporting
   aeronautical products and special requirements of importing authorities
   Parts Manufacturer Approvals Listing Listing of PMA holders and part
   numbers
   Repair Station Listing of aircraft associated repair stations
   Service Difficulty / Malfunction or Defect Reporting Service difficulty
   / malfunction or defect submission, query and reference
   Service Difficulty Reports Summaries Annual summaries of aircraft
   systems malfunctions, updated weekly
   Special Airworthiness Information Bulletins Aircraft certification
   information not regulatory in nature
   Supplemental Type Certificates After market additions or changes to
   aircraft
   Technical Standard Order A listing of technical standard orders issued
   by the FAA
   Type Certificate Data Sheets Shows the conditions and limitations of
   aircraft operation

